The Secret Sisters – Paperweight live in The Current studio
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube  

The Secret Sisters’ fifth studio album, "Mind, Man, Medicine," released on March 29, 2024, on New West Records. As part of the record release, The Secret Sisters — Laura Rogers and Lydia Slagle — visited the Twin Cities in May for two sold-out shows at the Parkway Theater in Minneapolis. Between shows, The Secret Sisters visited The Current for a session hosted by Bill DeVille. Watch The Secret Sisters' perform "Paperweight" above.

Musicians
Laura Rogers – vocals
Lydia Slagle – guitar, vocals
